            <div type="a">
                <column>7</column>
                <head>Now is the Time to Pay Debts</head>
                <origin>Prairie Farmer</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"It will be a glorious epoch when the people of these prairies own their
                    farms, and this we believe may at once be, if proper advantage be taken of the
                    times in which we now live."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Suggests that these inflationary times are ideal for the farmer trying to
                    get out of debt.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
